    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, fading paint on the hood, and a few small dings, though it remains structurally sound. Inside, the cabin is intact but shows clear signs of use, including some wear on the upholstery and minor staining on the carpets. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation.",
