    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in flawless, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects exacting care, from the unblemished exterior to the pristine, factory-fresh interior. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a specimen of unrivaled integrity and mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 47500.0,
